class="CybotCookiebotFader CybotCookiebotDialogActive" style="background-image: linear-gradient(to top, rgb(255, 255, 255), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0));"></div><h2 id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyContentTitle" lang="en">Responsible use of your data</h2><div id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyContentText" lang="en">We and <a id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyContentTextShowIABVendors" href="#">our partners</a> process your personal data, e.g. your IP-address, using technology such as cookies to store and access information on your device in order to serve personalized ads and content, ad and content measurement, audience insights and product development. You have a choice in who uses your data and for what purposes.<br><br><span id="CybotCookiebotDialogSpecialFeaturesText">If you allow, we would also like to: <ul><li>Collect information about your geographical location which can be accurate to within several meters</li><li>Identify your device by actively scanning it for specific characteristics (fingerprinting)</li></ul></span>Find out more about how your personal data is processed and set your preferences in the <a id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyContentTextToggleDetails" href="#">details section</a>. You can change or withdraw your consent any time from the Cookie Declaration.<br><br>Cookies are small text files that can be used by websites to make a user's experience more efficient.<br style=""><br style="">The law states that we can store cookies on your device if they are strictly necessary for the operation of this site. For all other types of cookies we need your permission.<br style=""><br style="">This site uses different types of cookies. Some cookies are placed by third party services that appear on our pages.<br style=""><br style="">You may read more about our use of cookies in the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.hltv.org/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>.<br style=""><br style="">Learn more about who we are, how you can contact us and how we process personal data in our Privacy Policy.<br style=""><br style="">Please state your consent ID and date when you contact us regarding your consent.</div></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyBottomWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2TabsIntro"><h2>About Ad Settings</h2>We and our advertising partners process your personal data using technology such as cookies in order to serve advertising, analyse our traffic and deliver customised experiences for you. You have a choice in who uses your data and for what purposes.</div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2TabsIntro">Some partners do not ask for your consent to process your data, instead, they rely on their legitimate business interest. <a id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderViewPartnersLink" href="#">View our list of partners</a> to see the purposes they believe they have legitimate interest for and how you can object to it.</div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2TabsIntro">Find out more about how your personal data is processed and set your preferences below.</div><div class="CookieCard"><div id="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2PurposesCard"><button id="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2Purposes" class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2Tab CybotCookiebotDialogCollapsed" tabindex="0" data-target="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2PurposesBody" lang="en" aria-label="Purposes<span class='CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount'>12</span>" aria-controls="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2PurposesBody">Purposes<span class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount">12</span></button><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2CardIntro">You can set your consent preferences and determine how you want your data to be used based on the purposes below. Each purpose has a description so that you know how we and our partners use your data. You can object to legitimate interest processing per purpose.</div></div><div id="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2PurposesBody" class="CollapseCard CybotCookiebotDialogHide" aria-labelledby="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2PurposesCard" aria-expanded="false"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeader">Purposes<span class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount">10</span><span class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderToggle"><a class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderButton select" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderToggleSelectAllPurposesLink" href="#">Accept all</a> <a class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderButton reject" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderToggleDeselectAllPurposesLink" href="#">Reject all</a></span></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose1" data-iabpurposeid="1" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose1">Store and/or access information on a device</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">Vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Store and access information on the device such as cookies and device identifiers presented to a user.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose2" data-iabpurposeid="2" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose2">Select basic ads</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest2" data-iabpurposeid="2" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest2">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To do basic ad selection vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Use real-time information about the context in which the ad will be shown, to show the ad, including information about the content and the device, such as: device type and capabilities, user agent, URL, IP address
</li><li>Use a user’s non-precise geolocation data
</li><li>Control the frequency of ads shown to a user.
</li><li>Sequence the order in which ads are shown to a user.
</li><li>Prevent an ad from serving in an unsuitable editorial (brand-unsafe) context
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Create a personalised ads profile using this information for the selection of future ads without a separate legal basis to create a personalised ads profile.
</li><li>N.B. Non-precise means only an approximate location involving at least a radius of 500 meters is permitted.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose3" data-iabpurposeid="3" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose3">Create a personalised ads profile</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest3" data-iabpurposeid="3" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest3">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To create a personalised ads profile vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Collect information about a user, including a user's activity, interests, demographic information, or location, to create or edit a user profile for use in personalised advertising.
</li><li>Combine this information with other information previously collected, including from across websites and apps, to create or edit a user profile for use in personalised advertising.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose4" data-iabpurposeid="4" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose4">Select personalised ads</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest4" data-iabpurposeid="4" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest4">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To select personalised ads vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Select personalised ads based on a user profile or other historical user data, including a user’s prior activity, interests, visits to sites or apps, location, or demographic information.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose5" data-iabpurposeid="5" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose5">Create a personalised content profile</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest5" data-iabpurposeid="5" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest5">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To create a personalised content profile vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Collect information about a user, including a user's activity, interests, visits to sites or apps, demographic information, or location, to create or edit a user profile for personalising content.
</li><li>Combine this information with other information previously collected, including from across websites and apps, to create or edit a user profile for use in personalising content.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose6" data-iabpurposeid="6" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose6">Select personalised content</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest6" data-iabpurposeid="6" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest6">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To select personalised content vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Select personalised content based on a user profile or other historical user data, including a user’s prior activity, interests, visits to sites or apps, location, or demographic information.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose7" data-iabpurposeid="7" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose7">Measure ad performance</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest7" data-iabpurposeid="7" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest7">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To measure ad performance vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Measure whether and how ads were delivered to and interacted with by a user
</li><li>Provide reporting about ads including their effectiveness and performance
</li><li>Provide reporting about users who interacted with ads using data observed during the course of the user's interaction with that ad
</li><li>Provide reporting to publishers about the ads displayed on their property
</li><li>Measure whether an ad is serving in a suitable editorial environment (brand-safe) context
</li><li>Determine the percentage of the ad that had the opportunity to be seen and the duration of that opportunity
</li><li>Combine this information with other information previously collected, including from across websites and apps
Vendors cannot:
*Apply panel- or similarly-derived audience insights data to ad measurement data without a Legal Basis to apply market research to generate audience insights (Purpose 9)</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose8" data-iabpurposeid="8" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose8">Measure content performance</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest8" data-iabpurposeid="8" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest8">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To measure content performance vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Measure and report on how content was delivered to and interacted with by users.
</li><li>Provide reporting, using directly measurable or known information, about users who interacted with the content
</li><li>Combine this information with other information previously collected, including from across websites and apps.
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Measure whether and how ads (including native ads) were delivered to and interacted with by a user.
</li><li>Apply panel- or similarly derived audience insights data to ad measurement data without a Legal Basis to apply market research to generate audience insights (Purpose 9)</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose9" data-iabpurposeid="9" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose9">Apply market research to generate audience insights</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest9" data-iabpurposeid="9" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest9">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To apply market research to generate audience insights vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Provide aggregate reporting to advertisers or their representatives about the audiences reached by their ads, through panel-based and similarly derived insights.
</li><li>Provide aggregate reporting to publishers about the audiences that were served or interacted with content and/or ads on their property by applying panel-based and similarly derived insights.
</li><li>Associate offline data with an online user for the purposes of market research to generate audience insights if vendors have declared to match and combine offline data sources (Feature 1)
</li><li>Combine this information with other information previously collected including from across websites and apps.
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Measure the performance and effectiveness of ads that a specific user was served or interacted with, without a Legal Basis to measure ad performance.
</li><li>Measure which content a specific user was served and how they interacted with it, without a Legal Basis to measure content performance.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose10" data-iabpurposeid="10" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposes" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurpose10">Develop and improve products</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest10" data-iabpurposeid="10" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonPurposesLegitimateInterestSelection" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABPurposeLegitimateInterest10">Legitimate Interest</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To develop new products and improve products vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Use information to improve their existing products with new features and to develop new products
</li><li>Create new models and algorithms through machine learning
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Conduct any other data processing operation allowed under a different purpose under this purpose</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeader" style="margin-top:12px;border-top:none">Special Purposes<span class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount">2</span></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel">Ensure security, prevent fraud, and debug</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To ensure security, prevent fraud and debug vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Ensure data are securely transmitted
</li><li>Detect and prevent malicious, fraudulent, invalid, or illegal activity.
</li><li>Ensure correct and efficient operation of systems and processes, including to monitor and enhance the performance of systems and processes engaged in permitted purposes
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Conduct any other data processing operation allowed under a different purpose under this purpose.
Note: Data collected and used to ensure security, prevent fraud, and debug may include automatically-sent device characteristics for identification, precise geolocation data, and data obtained by actively scanning device characteristics for identification without separate disclosure and/or opt-in.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel">Technically deliver ads or content</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">To deliver information and respond to technical requests vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Use a user’s IP address to deliver an ad over the internet
</li><li>Respond to a user’s interaction with an ad by sending the user to a landing page
</li><li>Use a user’s IP address to deliver content over the internet
</li><li>Respond to a user’s interaction with content by sending the user to a landing page
</li><li>Use information about the device type and capabilities for delivering ads or content, for example, to deliver the right size ad creative or video file in a format supported by the device
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Conduct any other data processing operation allowed under a different purpose under this purpose</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class="CookieCard"><div id="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2FeaturesCard"><button id="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2Features" class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2Tab CybotCookiebotDialogCollapsed" tabindex="0" data-target="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2FeaturesBody" lang="en" aria-label="Features<span class='CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount'>5</span>" aria-controls="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2FeaturesBody">Features<span class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount">5</span></button><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2CardIntro">View the required features enabled for the processing of personal data and opt-in separately for any special features.</div></div><div id="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2FeaturesBody" class="CollapseCard CybotCookiebotDialogHide" aria-labelledby="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBodyContentIABv2FeaturesCard" aria-expanded="false"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeader">Features<span class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount">3</span></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel">Match and combine offline data sources</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">Vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Combine data obtained offline with data collected online in support of one or more Purposes or Special Purposes.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel">Link different devices</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">Vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Deterministically determine that two or more devices belong to the same user or household
</li><li>Probabilistically determine that two or more devices belong to the same user or household
</li><li>Actively scan device characteristics for identification for probabilistic identification if users have allowed vendors to actively scan device characteristics for identification (Special Feature 2)</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel">Receive and use automatically-sent device characteristics for identification</label></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">Vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Create an identifier using data collected automatically from a device for specific characteristics, e.g. IP address, user-agent string.
</li><li>Use such an identifier to attempt to re-identify a device.
Vendors cannot:
</li><li>Create an identifier using data collected via actively scanning a device for specific characteristics, e.g. installed font or screen resolution without users’ separate opt-in to actively scanning device characteristics for identification.
</li><li>Use such an identifier to re-identify a device.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeader" style="margin-top:12px;border-top:none">Special Features<span class="CybotCookiebotDialogDetailBulkConsentCount">2</span><span class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderToggle"><a class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderButton select" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderToggleSelectAllFeaturesLink" href="#">Accept all</a> <a class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderButton reject" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABHeaderToggleDeselectAllFeaturesLink" href="#">Reject all</a></span></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABFeature1" data-iabspecialfeatureid="1" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonFeatures" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABFeature1">Use precise geolocation data</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">Vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Collect and process precise geolocation data in support of one or more purposes.
N.B. Precise geolocation means that there are no restrictions on the precision of a user’s location; this can be accurate to within several meters.</li></ul></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainer"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABContainerTogglesWrapper"><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonWrapper"><input type="checkbox" id="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABFeature2" data-iabspecialfeatureid="2" class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButton CybotCookiebotDialogBodyIABButtonFeatures" checked="checked" tabindex="0"><label class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABLabel" for="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABFeature2">Actively scan device characteristics for identification</label></div></div><div class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABDescription">Vendors can:
<ul class="CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonIABBullet"><li>Create an identifier using data collected via actively scanning a device for specific characteristics, e.g. installed fonts or screen resolution.
